{
  "body": "## The problem\r\n\r\nTests use different code and even tests for collecting pod6 or other kind of files, with exclusions also taking different forms. Most use `ends-with: `.pod6' so maybe this should be folded back into the auxiliary program\r\n\r\n\r\n## Suggestions\r\n\r\nAdd  `documents` or `pods` to `Test-Files` so that they can be used directly from test scripts.\r\n",
